// Platform extraction scripts — one directory per platform
// Each implements the ExtractionScript interface from docs/ARCHITECTURE.md §4.3
//
// Implemented in M1 (US) and M4 (CN):
//   amazon-us/    — Amazon US extraction
//   google-trends/ — Google Trends extraction
//   alibaba/      — Alibaba supplier search (US market sourcing signal)
//   taobao/       — Taobao (CN market, M4)
//   jd/           — JD.com (CN market, M4)
//   shopee/       — Shopee (SEA market)
//
// To add a new platform: create [platform-id]/index.ts, implement ExtractionScript,
// register in ExtractionScriptRegistry. No other files change.
